[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=MCNF Launcher
Comment=Mesh-wide app launcher — local apps, peers, workloads, services (Front Door)
# APPLAUNCH-9 (2026-06-27) — the standalone mde-apps-applet was RETIRED; the
# launcher role folded into the Front Door (one launcher). The Start button + the
# Super-key shortcut now open the Front Door's unified launcher panel via the
# workbench focus deep-link (the SOLE launcher trigger). No X-CosmicApplet — this
# is a plain launcher (a panel launcher button / keybinding runs it), not an
# in-panel applet that draws its own dropdown.
Exec=mde-workbench --focus launcher
Icon=magic-mesh
Terminal=false
Categories=COSMIC;System;
